name: MUFC Token
description: Built by the fan community, Manchester United Fan Token (MUFC) is a cryptocurrency representing voting rights in distribution mechanism as well as various benefits and rewards for holders, which they can leverage to engage and express the love to the Manchester United F.C. football club With the big love and loyal heart for MU, we desire to build the connection between fans around the world through MUFC token! Our ambition is to distribute MUFC token for all fans around the world and give control of those tokens to them.
